Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最討厭和最喜歡產生的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是兩個人的推理和懸疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.30,0:00:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和小蘭一起去紐約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女影星是整個事件的開端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.40,0:00:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.80,0:01:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這哪有什麼理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.80,0:02:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上真的有上帝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 天使從來沒有對我微笑過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.20,0:02:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 是那個時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一也在的 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.60,0:02:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一NY事件（事件篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.50,0:02:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點 喂 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.80,0:03:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.10,0:03:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.30,0:03:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭…小蘭姐姐她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 燒得那麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和醫院連絡一下 我們馬上過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 警官 哪個醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跨海大橋過去不是就有一家急救醫院嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有我認識的醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就可以準備好床位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐警車過去不用十分鐘就能到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先去把車發動起來 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.90,0:03:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新一嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.20,0:04:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不甘心啊  又被你救了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是在我最痛苦的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像能看穿我的內心一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很不甘心 但是好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.40,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 那不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Statue of Liberty
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本叫作自由女神像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過在紐約好像被叫作Miss Liberty
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 為什麼不把我叫起來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想從這座布魯克林大橋上看曼哈頓的夜景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多都錯過了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.40,0:05:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫妳在飛機上不好好睡 所以現在才會睏得睡著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了那種案件怎麼可能還睡得著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和某位看穿了一切真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就滿意地呼呼大睡的偵探不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有滿足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若想要達到推理和分析的顛峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.30,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使用盡一生也不夠喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.80,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,華生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.50,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種全世界戀人都想來的戀愛聖地吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人嫉妒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老媽妳也很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本是明天才來紐約的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻一到洛杉磯馬上又轉機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為已經沒希望的歌舞劇的票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？歌舞劇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.10,0:06:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.60,0:06:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 最近這裡很流行的Golden Apple啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 百老匯的魅影劇院 晚上八點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:35.20,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom：魅影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人期待呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸 你不覺得從剛才開始警車就挺多的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 一定是為了那個殺人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺人狂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.50,0:06:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是以年輕女子為目標的殺人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是日裔男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.00,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個殺人狂只在午夜十二點後才出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要在那之前回旅館的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會遇到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不到六點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是七點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是夏時制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.70,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我完全忘了還有夏時制這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從四月的第一個星期日開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提前一個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好著急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這座橋到魅影劇院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開車只要四十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不到七點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綽綽有餘不會遲到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟拿票的人約好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在開演前一個小時前到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以帶我們參觀後台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳就放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照媽媽的興趣買的這輛英國大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對來不及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是你說的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會再慢慢欣賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美洲豹公司推出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這輛美洲豹E型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別小看它喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車不是上個月剛修過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛拿回來不久嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓這邊的技師修理以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全復活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,276匹馬力的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.40,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有Le Mans比賽中獲得優勝的輪軸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.10,0:09:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止啦 警車會追來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 他們在反向車道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他們看到這優雅的車體時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們早就消失不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.60,0:09:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一和小蘭不來一下那個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的彎道可能有些困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小蘭 過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 哦 什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一開始的時候會覺得害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要緊緊地抓住我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看 沒什麼大不了的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫沒有什麼大不了的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好提前一個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 毫無問題的安全到達了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.30,0:10:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請出示妳的駕駛執照跟入境許可證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.25,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Your license and registration,please!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.80,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超速四十公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:20.00,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,40 miles over the speed limit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是在扮演「緊急追捕令」的男主角嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.64,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing Dirty Harry?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我們有急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.39,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,we are in a hurry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪裡見過妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.72,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,You look familiar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…你大概是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.22,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,you might…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大概是在哪個案件見過她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.61,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have met her in some case.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.98,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she works with us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長官！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.11,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個臥底警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.73,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an undercover agent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.57,0:11:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子她把犯人跟丟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.57,0:11:45.17,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have missed the criminal…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個大叔是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉迪修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.40,0:11:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,優作以前幫他們破案時認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紐約市的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉迪修·雷伍得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妻子是日本人 所以他日語也很棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了 拉迪修 你可幫了大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.20,0:12:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 你謝錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 謝錯人了是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.10,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要謝的話 能不能謝我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.30,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要謝的話 能不能謝我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.10,0:12:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.00,0:12:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向我這位莎朗·溫亞德道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎…莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.50,0:13:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個警官是我的影迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在等妳的時候和他聊了一下天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的對講機就響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是一輛銀色的車子以不得了的速度往這裡開過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是我就穿上他的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,易容成了拉迪修警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.10,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件男士外套很貴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.30,0:13:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 沒關係嗎 很多人在看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 不會有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經跟大家說是在拍電影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我最喜歡莎朗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.40,0:13:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 媽媽啊 拜託妳告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 新一不認識嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國的超人氣女影星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:14:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才要問為什麼這個女影星能喬裝成別人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸？ 我以前沒跟你說過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛出道的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經出演一名女間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠演好這個角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.90,0:14:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就去向一位著名的日本魔術師拜師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學習易容術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗也是為了同樣的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個魔術師那裡學習易容術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是我們就成了好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.70,0:14:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我不能像莎朗那樣扮誰像誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 媽媽那種胡亂扮演的與其說是易容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不如說是變裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊 我的是變裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是變裝 我也是很認真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好棒 能遇到這樣的名人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是在紐約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要好好感謝上帝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上真的有上帝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的有上帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.80,0:15:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些拚命努力的人就不會有不幸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.50,0:15:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 至少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.50,0:15:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使從來沒有對我微笑過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那悲哀的微笑說不定正暗示著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來發生的慘劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不願回想起來的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那讓人討厭的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼天使從來沒有對妳微笑過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是說一直很辛苦的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生只不過是不幸的連續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「逝去的思念」公演當天 父母死於火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獲得奧斯卡獎的第二天 丈夫病死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.40,0:16:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟作為我的女兒才一出道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就備受寵愛的克莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.20,0:16:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是妳引以為傲自豪的女兒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.70,0:16:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩 我已經不當她是女兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳相信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她易容成我丈夫的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我掃墓的時候 站在我的身後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我丈夫一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是玩笑 妳不覺得太過分了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 話說回來 莎朗妳說過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女兒死纏著妳要學易容術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那孩子也就到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經快十年沒見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.90,0:17:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說她最近和一些壞朋友在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.60,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.50,0:17:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該把車停到停車場 去後台了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.30,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人也開始發現這裡沒有攝影機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼一定要在開演前一個小時來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早一點來的話也不會打擾到他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以輕鬆的聊天不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.50,0:17:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早點來見到的他們 也不過是普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開演前的話 呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 那不是莎朗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員難得也會說真話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.30,0:18:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 好感動 好像做夢一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得有空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.20,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,如何 一起去吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.50,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.90,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開演前化了妝才變成了演員呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很崇拜莎朗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.50,0:18:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她跟這個劇團的管理員是熟人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說要來看 很容易就拿到票了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.30,0:18:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.70,0:18:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那個人該不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.20,0:18:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 退隱前大受歡迎的女偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜男爵夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.00,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Night Baroness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.40,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.80,0:18:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜男爵夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.70,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 媽媽在這邊是這樣被稱呼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是暗夜男爵的作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤優作的妻子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.20,0:19:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽有一次在這裡的電視搜查節目中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.60,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以推理小說家妻子的身分出場過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.10,0:19:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那個時候的推理全部都說中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就很快抓到了犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.50,0:19:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後就被稱作女偵探暗夜男爵夫人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正那些推理 也只不過是把爸爸每天早上看報紙時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.20,0:19:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自言自語的推理照樣說出來罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人是你的孩子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男孩的確是 女孩就不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.70,0:19:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說不定以後會是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.70,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.10,0:19:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.10,0:19:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 原來以為暗夜男爵夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了解開那個奇怪的包裹謎團而來的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果只是為了來說說笑笑罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是失望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的包裹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天前這個劇院收到了一個包裹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塗上了金色顏料的蘋果──Golden Apple
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面還用動物的血寫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.30,0:20:22.40,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,For the Fairest
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.30,0:20:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獻給最美麗的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.00,0:20:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走進後台的時候就覺得氣氛有些奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是因為這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.90,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 不要慌張 我的女神們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是惡作劇罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個劇場的首席明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西斯·弗洛克哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為決定要出演電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像是最後一次出演歌舞劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.80,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 轉變一下心情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著莎朗的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看我們舞台的內部吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離開演前只有四十五分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還來這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始的二十分鐘只不過是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.70,0:21:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡單介紹一下這個歌舞劇的原著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.30,0:21:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個希臘神話罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天花板上的那個是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.00,0:21:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 舞台服裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了節省地方 就吊在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.40,0:21:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.40,0:21:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.30,0:21:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盔甲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.10,0:21:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.50,0:21:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.50,0:21:45.00,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.20,0:22:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.10,0:23:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.40,0:23:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 小蘭拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.50,0:23:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.10,0:24:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.10,0:24:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經逃走了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.60,0:24:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.20,0:24:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.50,0:24:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一NY事件（推理篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.30,0:24:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.80,0:24:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.70,0:24:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我要開始推理了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.70,0:24:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不好好推理的話還會變小的喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.50,0:24:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.80,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:27.57,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們兩人所訴說的未來裡 就像有你在身邊的棲身地一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.10,0:00:31.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.87,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,把我當作是你的全部喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.57,0:00:43.05,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,相信兩個人牽著的手 發誓我們一起走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.16,0:00:49.89,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,“最討厭” 即使是謊言我也說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.92,0:00:56.94,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,“最喜歡” 如果不是謊言我就不會說喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.68,0:01:05.11,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無法見面的時候 你就像無暇考慮其他東西一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.39,0:01:10.81,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的心裡只有我 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.48,0:01:14.87,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.02,0:01:24.42,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓兩個愛永不分離 請緊緊擁抱對方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.24,0:01:31.56,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此不安的夜晚 還是會來臨的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.58,0:01:39.65,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,840)}那時候 要緊緊地擁抱我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.17,0:22:27.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,每個清晨來臨的時候都會想起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.55,0:22:33.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只要在你身旁就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.84,0:22:39.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕因時間的流逝而哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.19,0:22:45.17,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在漸漸改變的人的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.86,0:22:58.76,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有期望也就不會失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.58,0:23:05.55,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,然而不能沒有追求啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.84,0:23:12.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無論前方的道路是何等艱辛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.80,0:23:20.02,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在夢醒以後 你還是那麼遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.23,0:23:25.55,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是自作多情的徒勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.77,0:23:33.16,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,花雨中的道路還是沒有絲毫改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.40,0:23:40.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,880)}真想挽著你的手漫步其中啊
